text: Warlock is a 1959 American western movie directed by Edward Dmytryk and was based on the 1958 novel of the same name. It stars Henry Fonda, Richard Widmark, Anthony Quinn, DeForest Kelley, Wallace Ford, Tom Drake, Richard Arlen, Whit Bissell and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1959 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Edward Dmytryk Category:Movies set in Utah Category:Movies composed by Leigh Harline
